ter — Star Atlas</figcaption></figure><p id="ee0b" class="pw-post-body-paragraph jv jw iy jx b jy jz ka kb kc kd ke kf kg kh ki kj kk kl km kn ko kp kq kr ks ir ga"><strong class="jx iz">Commander</strong>: <strong class="jx iz">FIMBUL BYOS Tankship</strong></p><figure class="lk ll lm ln gx lo gl gm paragraph-image"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="lp lq do lr ce ls"><div class="gl gm lz"><picture><source data-testid="og" srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/max/640/0*d2Tm3NE18kpeSlNl 640w, https://miro.medium.com/max/720/0*d2Tm3NE18kpeSlNl 720w, https://miro.medium.com/max/750/0*d2Tm3NE18kpeSlNl 750w, https://miro.medium.com/max/786/0*d2Tm3NE18kpeSlNl 786w, https://miro.medium.com/max/828/0*d2Tm3NE18kpeSlNl 828w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1100/0*d2Tm3NE18kpeSlNl 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/0*d2Tm3NE18kpeSlNl 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"/><img alt="" class="ce lt lu c" width="700" height="283" loading="lazy" role="presentation"/></picture></div></div><figcaption class="lv bl gn gl gm lw lx bm b bn bo cn">Fimbul BYOS Tankship Fighter — Star Atlas</figcaption></figure><p id="c0b9" class="pw-post-body-paragraph jv jw iy jx b jy jz ka kb kc kd ke kf kg kh ki kj kk kl km kn ko kp kq kr ks ir ga">Its no surprise that the most powerful ships for value are fighter ships. Again, dont feel like you have to buy fighters if your goal is to manufacture and transport in the game. Then again, your fleets may need protection at some point and its always good to know which ships are the best out there.</p><p id="8669" class="pw-post-body-paragraph jv jw iy jx b jy jz ka kb kc kd ke kf kg kh ki kj kk kl km kn ko kp kq kr ks ir ga">Do you agree or disagree with the ratings? Leave a comment below and don’t forget to hit follow for more Star Atlas news and coverage.</p></div><div class="o dx ma mb id mc" role="separator"><span class="md fl ci me mf mg"></span><span class="md fl ci me mf mg"></span><span class="md fl ci me mf"></span></div><div class="ir is it iu iv"><p id="589c" class="pw-post-body-paragraph jv jw iy jx b jy jz ka kb kc kd ke kf kg kh ki kj kk kl km kn ko kp kq kr ks ir ga">Krigs is the founder of The Hologram News Network, an independent blockchain gaming meta-news organization devoted to the coverage of the Star Atlas game. Krigs has covered Star Atlas for the past year and enjoys writing about the potential that blockchain technology has to revolutionize the gaming industry.</p><p id="257d" class="pw-post-body-paragraph jv jw iy jx b jy jz ka kb kc kd ke kf kg kh ki kj kk kl km kn ko kp kq kr ks ir ga">Follow on Social Media:</p><p id="5b41" class="pw-post-body-paragraph jv jw iy jx b jy jz ka kb kc kd ke kf kg kh ki kj kk kl km kn ko kp kq kr ks ir ga">Krigs: <a class="au mh" href="https://twitter.com/Krigsfoniks" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">https://twitter.com/Krigsfoniks</a><br/>The Hologram: <a class="au mh" href="https://twitter.com/Hologram_News" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">https://twitter.com/Hologram_News</a></p></div></div></section></div></div></article><div class="mi o"></div></div></div><div class="l"></div><footer class="mj mk ml mm o ao mn mo c"><div class="l mp"><div class="o dx"><div class="em ce fa fb fc fd fe ff fg fh fi"><div class="o u mq"><div class="o ao hc"><div class="mr l"><span class="l he ms mt e d"><div class="o ao hc"><div class="pw-multi-vote-icon do mu mv mw mx"><div class=""><div class="dr my de mz na nb nc bb nd ne nf mx"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-label="clap"><